DTSTAMP:20251106T142257Z
SUMMARY:Summer shift: heat, airflow, deep watering
DESCRIPTION:Dial in airflow indoors, watch basil and Calathea closely, and ensure young trees get deep, infrequent soaks during hot, dry weeks.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20250615T190000
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=6;BYMONTHDAY=15
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
