DTSTAMP:20251106T142257Z
SUMMARY:Fall shift: taper feeding, set buds, water before freeze
DESCRIPTION:Begin Christmas cactus bud-set routine, taper indoor fertilizer, and deep-water young trees until the soil begins to freeze.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20250915T190000
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=9;BYMONTHDAY=15
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
