DTSTAMP:20251106T142257Z
SUMMARY:Winter shift: low light, dry air, frozen soil
DESCRIPTION:Cluster plants in brightest windows, pause fertilizer, and on mild days with thawed ground consider a deep drink for young evergreens and crabapples if it’s been dry.
DTSTART;TZID=America/Chicago:20251201T190000
RRULE:FREQ=YEARLY;BYMONTH=12;BYMONTHDAY=1
